Author: CeslieLondon
Text: My over the moon happy was 120. Then I did 115 because I was chasing the high. Now it’s 105. If I ever get double digits I think I’ll break down. But a part of me is curious :(

Author: x24throwaway
Text: This is a mood. I’ve had an ED for 11 years and every gw I’ve ever had, this has happened. It changes just as I’m almost there. I’m approaching my ugw and I’m starting to think about lowering it. Literally the goal I’ve had for a decade and now that I’m almost there I want to lower it.   It’ll never be enough.
